  "prompt": "How do I know what he feels about me?",
  "response": "To understand someone's feelings, pay attention to these signs:\n\n1. Communication cues\n- How often he contacts you\n- Quality of conversations\n- His level of engagement\n\n2. Body language\n- Eye contact\n- Physical proximity\n- Subtle touches\n- Facial expressions\n\n3. Actions\n- Makes time for you\n- Shows interest in your life\n- Remembers details you've shared\n- Goes out of his way to help you\n\n4. Verbal indicators\n- Compliments\n- Talks about future plans together\n- Shares personal thoughts/feelings\n- Asks about your life\n\n5. Direct communication\n- Best way is to have an honest conversation\n- Ask him about his feelings\n- Express your own feelings\n\n6. Watch for consistent behavior\n- Consistent attention and effort\n- Reliability and dependability\n\n7. Trust your instincts\n- Sometimes you can sense genuine feelings\n- Pay attention to how you feel around him\n\nRemember, everyone expresses feelings differently. The best approach is usually open, honest communication.",
